title: Akuyaku Reijou nanode Last Boss wo Kattemimashita
synopsis: Being acutely ill, a young girl has spent most of her life in a hospital room playing otome games to fill her time. However, she one day finds herself in the midst of a scene from one of these games as the story's villainess, Irene Loren D'Autriche.
